{
  "texts": [
    "By reusing convolutional units, the proposed model reduces the network size and achieves better results.",
    "It is difficult to optimize feature maps due to the large number of filters included in the convolution node.",
    "To decrease the network size while maintaining the quality of the feature map, double blocks have been used.",
    "In comparison with the current model, the introduced model yields improved outcomes with a reduced size.",
    "The outcomes determine the effectiveness of the introduced model in polyp segmentation."
  ]
}